reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 27, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Absolutely love this dresser. It's so pretty and easy to assemble. Draws are big and can store a lot. Not to mention the fabric on the front of the draws are so soft! Love it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 15, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Bedroom dresser with led
reviews.reviewText: This is a very pretty bedroom dresser with led. The quality is very good and the surface is very smooth. Size is perfect and it's not big or too tall. It's perfect for my 8 years old son. He uses partial to storage his own valuable items and Legos.Assembly was not hard but it's time consuming. The instructions was very clear and well illustrated. I used the manual hand too and it took me 2 hours to put together. It does need a lot of patience to put it together. It will be really fast if you have electronic too and it will speed up the installation process. Overall, good value and good quality.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 10, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice little clothing drawer for bedrooms
reviews.reviewText: It's a nice sized clothing drawer for bedrooms. I personally use mine to hold onto all of my socks, underwear, and shorts and pajamas. It feels relatively sturdy, but it definitely feels like if I'm not careful when opening it that I can cause it to topple over if I'm opening the drawers too quickly and strongly.But it's got a lot of storage space and it looks relatively nice as well for giving yourself some more storage to organize a bedroom or a closet with. Additionally while it's taller, the drawers aren't super long as they are wide so you can definitely fit this dresser into smaller spaces.

reviews.reviewText: I assembled this in less than 30 minutes. I just moved into a studio apartment & plan to put it in my bathroom to hold my towels.
